Powell Capital Markets, Inc. is a
			full-service regional investment banking firm headquartered in
			Roseland, New Jersey. Founded in August 1990, the firm provides
			investment banking, private placements, financial advisory, and
			lease financing services to public entities. Our broad range of
			clients consists of states, cities, counties, school districts,
			local authorities, commissions, hospitals, prisons, and higher
			educational institutions.

			Powell Capital Markets has specialized in public finance since its
			inception. Powell Capital Markets� core strategy has been to build
			strong relationships with clients by understanding their key goals
			and objectives. As a result, we have earned the confidence of our
			client base through significant repeat business over the past 26
			years.
Powell Capital Markets has the
			ability to market municipal obligations on a regional and national
			basis as a result of a full complement of institutional and dealer
			relationships that we have established over many years of selling
			and 
						underwriting municipal issues. This network of institutions and
			dealers, small and large, regional and national, provides us
						with access to a wide range of potential buyers at both the
			retail and institutional level.

						Our carefully cultivated institutional investors 
						augmented by our dealer network have come to rely on us 
						to supply them with New Jersey municipal investment 
						opportunities. In turn they provide us with significant 
						orders � an extremely valuable benefit to our clients.


















		All Rights reserved. Powell Capital Markets, Inc ., Member 
			FINRA and
			



