Career Opportunities

Powell Capital Markets, Inc. has built a commanding
					reputation over its 26+ year history through building
					businesses and hiring and engaging people who share our
					focus on pride in customer service and customer
					satisfaction. This approach shapes how we maximize
					relationships, how we promote our employees and the way we
					do business every day.
If you are confident, driven and have an excellent
					academic track record, the opportunities to advance your
					career are already in place at Powell Capital Markets, Inc.
Powell Capital Markets, Inc. is committed to hiring the
					best candidates, regardless of sex, age, race, religion,
					national origin, sexual preference, gender, or cultural
					differences.
Interested professionals should send their resume and
					cover letter to:
HR@powellcapital.com
					or fax to 973-740-1787.
Powell Capital Markets, Inc. is an equal opportunity
					employer.

















