Investment Banking
Powell Capital Markets� expertise spans the
			entire spectrum of taxable and tax-exempt financings, from
			negotiated general obligation and revenue bond financings to lease
			financings and private placements.
With
			over 26 years of experience, Powell Capital Markets has provided
			services for every size issuer. Our work has spanned:


School construction

Housing

Hospitals

Airports and transportation systems

Solid waste disposal systems

Water utilities

Resource recovery


			Powell Capital Markets� participation has
			included acting as sole manager, senior manager and co-manager.
The firm specializes in assisting clients with
			special credit needs such as first-time issuers, unrated entities,
			or those issuers with appropriation-only revenue streams.
Powell Capital Markets works with clients,
			rating agencies and investors to achieve the best possible outcome
			for their debt issuances . The caliber of Powell�s commitment to
			clients is highlighted in transactions where educating the market on
			a client�s credit can be an involved and lengthy process,
			culminating in a long-term benefit to the issuer for its ongoing
			capital needs.
			 

















