About
Powell Capital Markets Inc is located at the address 3 Becker Farm rd Ste 103 in Roseland, New Jersey 07068.  They can be contacted via phone at (973) 740-1230 for pricing, hours and directions.  Powell Capital Markets Inc has an annual sales volume of 501K - 999,999.  .For more information contact Romane  Willis, Manufacturing Supervisor or  go to www.powellcap.comPowell Capital Markets Inc provides Corporate Services, Long Term Planning, Wealth Management to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Powell Capital Markets Inc view the map to the right.  For reviews of Powell Capital Markets Inc see below.









