Industry: Institutional Financial Svcs
Sub-Industry: Institutional Brokerage
Powell Capital Markets, Inc. operates as an investment banking firm. The Firm offers private placements, financial advisory, and lease financing services. Powell Capital Markets serves public entities in the United States.




